The failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
The failure of the starter can cause the vehicle to be unable to start, leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the rear passenger door can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to safety issues if the door becomes stuck or opens while driving.
The engine stalling while driving can cause loss of control, accidents, and leave the driver stranded, potentially leading to safety risks.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while driving
the engine dies while in motion.
